OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones announce new album,
OL,4,CForeign Tongues
OL,6,FThe Rolling Stones have revealed that
OL,7,FForeign Tongues is the name of their
OL,8,Fnew album, after the legendary rock
OL,9,Fgroup spent weeks hinting at the
OL,10,Fannouncement.
OL,12,FThe band said the album will be
OL,13,Freleased on July 10 and feature 14
OL,14,Fsongs, with the first single, dubbed
OL,15,FIn the Stars, published on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
