OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones announce new album,
OL,4,CForeign Tongues
OL,6,FThe announcement comes after months of
OL,7,Fteasing by the rock group, through
OL,8,Fmysterious billboards and posts, which
OL,9,Fsparked rumours that the band would
OL,10,Frelease a new album ` their first
OL,11,Fsince their 2023 Grammy Award-winning
OL,12,Frecord Hackney Diamonds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
