PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778015468
OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones announce new album,
OL,4,CForeign Tongues
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, the band said the album
OL,7,Fwill feature performances from the
OL,8,Fcore band members as well as their key
OL,9,Fcollaborators, including Darryl Jones
OL,10,Fand Matt Clifford, as well as
OL,11,Fcontributions from Steve Winwood, Paul
OL,12,FMcCartney, The Cure's Robert Smith and
OL,13,FChad Smith of the Red Hot Chili
OL,14,FPeppers.
OL,16,FIt also includes a special appearance
OL,17,Ffrom Charlie Watts, captured during
OL,18,Fone of his final recording sessions
OL,19,Fbefore his passing in 2021
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
