OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778015468
OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones announce new album,
OL,4,CForeign Tongues
OL,6,FOn Saturday, band members Sir Mick
OL,7,FJagger, Ronnie Wood and Keith Richards
OL,8,Fshared the artwork for the album,
OL,9,Fwhich features an illustration of a
OL,10,Fcollage of a mismatched head.
OL,12,FOn Friday, the band shared a snippet
OL,13,Ffrom an unnamed song over a 13-second
OL,14,Fvideo to their 4.2 million fans of
OL,15,Ftheir signature tongue and lips logo
OL,16,Fon a moving background.
OL,18,FThe caption consisted of two emojis,
OL,19,Fincluding one of a CD, leading fans to
OL,20,Fbelieve they are hinting at a new
OL,21,Frecord.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
