OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones announce new album,
OL,4,CForeign Tongues
OL,6,FRumours of new music were first
OL,7,Fsparked last month when a series of
OL,8,Fcryptic messages including posters and
OL,9,FQR codes linked to The Cockroaches
OL,10,Fpopped up around London believed to be
OL,11,Fconnected to the band.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
