OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778015468
OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones announce new album,
OL,4,CForeign Tongues
OL,6,FThe Rolling Stones have also
OL,7,Freportedly released music and
OL,8,Fperformed gigs under the pseudonym,
OL,9,FThe Cockroaches, with teaser videos
OL,10,Fhinting at the name shared to their
OL,11,FInstagram.
OL,13,FThe Cockroaches later released a
OL,14,Flimited-edition vinyl single, titled
OL,15,FRough And Twisted on April 11, which
OL,16,Fwas reportedly only sold exclusively
OL,17,Fat independent record stores.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
