OL,3,CThe Rolling Stones announce new album,
OL,4,CForeign Tongues
OL,6,FFormed in London in 1962, The Rolling
OL,7,FStones have a long history of chart-
OL,8,Ftopping albums and number one singles,
OL,9,Fincluding (I Can't Get No)
OL,10,FSatisfaction, Paint It Black and Start
OL,11,FMe Up.
OL,13,FThroughout their decades-long career,
OL,14,FThe Rolling Stones have had 14 UK
OL,15,Fnumber one albums and eight number one
OL,16,Fhits.
OL,18,FThe rock band was inducted into the
OL,19,FRock and Roll Hall of Fame in 1989.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
